description.standard: After a string of powerful hit singles that showed off the strength and range of her voice (“Here,” “Scars to Your Beautiful,” “Stay”), Alessia Cara returns with something a little lighter. “October,” as charming and catchy as a John Mayer song, has the sort of simple, swaying melodies that linger in your brain long after the track has finished. Add it to your library now and subscribe to New Music Daily, Apple Music’s home for the latest must-hear songs.
description.short: A bittersweet pop song from Alessia Cara.
